Construct an endpoints collection from a dictionary.

Example:

    ```python
    {
      "endpoint-uuid-1": {
        "host_regex": "host1-regex",
        "endpoint_path": "/path/to/endpoint/dir",
        "local_path": "/path/to/local/dir"
      },
      "endpoint-uuid-2": {
        "host_regex": "host2-regex",
        "endpoint_path": "/path/to/endpoint/dir",
        "local_path": "/path/to/local/dir"
      }
    }
    ```
